icense was <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">refunded</span>.'=>'您的 %s 授權已<span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">退款</span>。','Please purchase a new license to continue receiving access to TranslatePress AI, premium addons, automatic updates and support.'=>'請購買新授權，以繼續取得 TranslatePress AI、進階附加元件、自動更新及支援的存取權限。','Purchase a new license'=>'購買新授權','Your %s license is <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">missing or invalid</span>.'=>'您的 %s 授權<span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">遺失或無效</span>。','Please enter a valid license to get access to TranslatePress AI, premium addons, automatic updates and support. Need a license key? %1$sPurchase one now%2$s'=>'請輸入有效的授權以使用 TranslatePress AI、進階附加元件、自動更新及支援。需要授權金鑰嗎？%1$s立即購買%2$s','Enter a valid license'=>'輸入有效授權','Slugs'=>'Slugs','Meta Information'=>'中繼資訊','String List'=>'字串清單','Gettext Strings'=>'Gettext 字串','Images'=>'圖片','Videos'=>'影片','Audios'=>'音訊','Dynamically Added Strings'=>'動態新增的字串','Translation Editor'=>'翻譯編輯器','Edit translations by visually selecting them on each site page'=>'在每個網站頁面上以視覺化選取方式編輯翻譯','String Translation'=>'字串翻譯','Edit url slug translations, plugins and theme translation (emails, forms etc.)'=>'編輯 URL slug 翻譯、外掛程式及佈景主題翻譯（電子郵件、表單等）','Current User'=>'目前使用者','Logged Out'=>'已登出','Translate Page'=>'翻譯頁面','Add a New Language'=>'新增語言','Get a Free AI License'=>'取得免費 AI 授權','Your License is Invalid'=>'您的授權無效','Get More AI Words (%d left)'=>'取得更多 AI 字數（剩餘 %d）','Opens post in the translation editor. Post must be saved as draft or published beforehand.'=>'在翻譯編輯器中開啟文章。文章必須事先儲存為草稿或發佈。','Security check'=>'安全性檢查','<strong>Warning:</strong> Some strings have possibly incorrectly encoded characters. This may result in breaking the queries, rendering the page untranslated in live mode. Consider revising the following strings or their method of outputting.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong> 部分字串可能包含編碼不正確的字元。這可能導致查詢錯誤，使頁面在正式環境中無法顯示翻譯。請考慮修改以下字串或其輸出方式。','TranslatePress data update'=>'TranslatePress 資料更新','We need to update your translations database to the latest version.'=>'我們需要將您的翻譯資料庫更新至最新版本。','Updating will allow editing translations of localized text from plugins and theme. Existing translation will still work as expected.'=>'更新後即可編輯外掛和佈景主題本地化文字的翻譯。現有翻譯仍會正常運作。','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!
Are you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要：強烈建議先備份資料庫！\\n您確定要繼續嗎？','Run the updater'=>'執行更新程式','Updating will allow editing translations of slugs. Existing translation will still work as expected.'=>'更新後將可編輯代稱的翻譯。現有的翻譯仍會正常運作。','Please activate the SEO Addon from <br/>WordPress -> Settings -> TranslatePress -> Addons section'=>'請從 <br/>WordPress -> 設定 -> TranslatePress -> 附加元件區段啟用 SEO 附加元件。','Go to Addons'=>'前往附加元件','The SEO Pack add-on allows translation of all the URL slugs:'=>'SEO Pack 附加元件可讓您翻譯所有 URL 代稱：','Taxonomy slugs'=>'分類法代稱','Term slugs'=>'詞彙代稱','Post slugs (this includes pages and custom post types)'=>'文章代稱（包含頁面和自訂文章類型）','Post type base slugs'=>'文章類型基底代稱','WooCommerce slugs'=>'WooCommerce 代稱','The SEO Pack add-on is available with ALL premium versions of the plugin.'=>'SEO Pack 附加元件適用於此外掛程式的所有進階版本。','Upgrade to Pro'=>'升級至專業版','Description'=>'描述','Article Section'=>'文章區段','Article Tag'=>'文章標籤','OG Title'=>'OG 標題','OG Site Name'=>'OG 網站名稱','OG Description'=>'OG 描述','OG Image Alt'=>'OG 圖片替代文字','Twitter Title'=>'Twitter 標題','Twitter Description'=>'Twitter 描述','Twitter Image Alt'=>'Twitter 圖片替代文字','Page Title'=>'頁面標題','Dublin Core Title'=>'Dublin Core 標題','Dublin Core Description'=>'Dublin Core 描述','OG Image'=>'OG 圖片','OG Image Secure URL'=>'OG 圖片安全 URL','Twitter Image'=>'Twitter 圖片','Removing cdata dictionary strings for language %s...'=>'正在移除語言 %s 的 CDATA 字典字串...','Removing untranslated dictionary links for language %s...'=>'正在移除語言 %s 的未翻譯字典連結...','Removing duplicated gettext strings for language %s...'=>'正在移除語言 %s 的重複 Gettext 字串...','Removing duplicated dictionary strings for language %s...'=>'正在移除語言 %s 的重複字典字串...','Removing untranslated dictionary strings where translation is available for language %s...'=>'正在移除語言 %s 中已有可用翻譯的未翻譯字典字串...','Inserting original strings for language %s...'=>'正在為語言 %s 插入原始字串...','Cleaning original strings table for language %s...'=>'正在清理語言 %s 的原始字串資料表...','Updating original string ids for language %s...'=>'正在更新語言 %s 的原始字串 ID...','Regenerating original meta table for language %s...'=>'正在重新產生語言 %s 的原始 meta 資料表...','Cleaning original meta table for language %s...'=>'正在清理語言 %s 的原始 meta 資料表...','Replacing original id NULL with value for language %s...'=>'正在將語言 %s 的原始 ID NULL 取代為值...','Inserting gettext original strings for language %s...'=>'正在為語言 %s 插入 Gettext 原始字串...','Cleaning gettext original strings table for language %s...'=>'正在清理語言 %s 的 Gettext 原始字串資料表...','Updating gettext original string ids for language %s...'=>'正在更新語言 %s 的 Gettext 原始字串 ID...','Migrating taxonomy and post type base slugs to new table structure...'=>'正在將分類法與文章類型基底代稱遷移至新的資料表結構...','Migrating post slugs to new table structure for language %s...'=>'正在將語言 %s 的文章代稱遷移至新的資料表結構...','Migrating term slugs to new table structure for language %s...'=>'正在將詞彙 slug 遷移至新資料表結構，語言為 %s...','Finishing up...'=>'正在完成...','Database optimization did not complete successfully. We recommend restoring the original database or <a href="%s" >trying again.</a>'=>'資料庫最佳化未能成功完成。建議還原原始資料庫，或<a href="%s" >再試一次。</a>','Update aborted! Your user account doesn\'t have the capability to perform database updates.'=>'更新已中止！您的使用者帳號沒有執行資料庫更新的權限。','Update aborted! Invalid nonce.'=>'更新已中止！nonce 無效。','Update aborted! Incorrect action.'=>'更新已中止！動作不正確。','Update aborted! Incorrect language code.'=>'更新已中止！語言代碼不正確。','Updating database to version %s+'=>'正在更新資料庫至版本 %s+','Processing table for language %s...'=>'正在處理語言 %s 的資料表...','Back to TranslatePress Settings'=>'返回 TranslatePress 設定','Successfully updated database!'=>'資料庫更新成功！',' done.'=>' 完成。','All individual TranslatePress add-on plugins <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">have been discontinued</a> and are now included in the premium Personal, Business and Developer versions of TranslatePress. Please log into your <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">account page</a>, download the new premium version and install it. Your individual addons settings will be ported over.'=>'所有獨立的 TranslatePress 附加元件外掛程式<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">已停止維護</a>，現已納入 TranslatePress 進階版個人版、商業版及開發者版本中。請登入您的<a href="%2$s" target="_blank">帳號頁面</a>，下載新的進階版本並安裝。您個別附加元件的設定將會被移轉過來。','Brand-new Language Switcher Settings are here!'=>'全新的語言切換器設定登場！','Explore pre-made templates, switch colors, flag styles, spacing, layouts & more. Use the live preview to perfect your switcher in seconds.'=>'探索預製範本、切換顏色、旗幟樣式、間距、版面配置及更多功能。使用即時預覽功能，在幾秒內將您的切換器調整至完美。','Start customizing'=>'開始自訂','Read documentation'=>'閱讀說明文件','TranslatePress'=>'TranslatePress','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> requires <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP library</a></strong>. Please contact your server administrator to install it on your server.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong> 需要 <strong><a href="http://php.net/manual/en/book.mbstring.php">Multibyte String PHP 函式庫</a></strong>。請聯絡您的伺服器管理員在伺服器上安裝此函式庫。','Detected long query limitation on WPEngine hosting. Some large pages may appear untranslated. You can remove limitation by adding the following to your site’s wp-config.php: define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false ); '=>'偵測到 WPEngine 主機上的長查詢限制。部分大型頁面可能會顯示為未翻譯。您可以透過在網站的 wp-config.php 中加入以下內容來移除限制：define( \'WPE_GOVERNOR\', false ); ','Custom Language Flag'=>'自訂語言旗幟','The Language code of the added custom language cannot be empty.'=>'新增的自訂語言之語言代碼不能為空白。','The Language code of the added custom language is invalid.'=>'新增的自訂語言之語言代碼無效。','The Automatic Translation Code of the added custom language is invalid.'=>'新增的自訂語言之自動翻譯代碼無效。','TranslatePress Add-ons'=>'TranslatePress 附加元件','You must first purchase this version to have access to the addon %1$shere%2$s'=>'您必須先購買此版本才能存取附加元件 %1$s此處%2$s','Please %1$senter your license%2$s key first, to activate this addon.'=>'請先%1$s輸入授權%2$s金鑰，以啟用此附加元件。','You need an active license to have access to the addon. Renew or purchase a new one %1$shere%2$s.'=>'您需要有效的授權才能存取此附加元件。請%1$s在此處%2$s續約或購買新授權。','Advanced Add-ons'=>'進階附加元件','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Developer, Business and Personal plans.'=>'這些附加元件可擴充您的翻譯外掛，適用於開發者、商業及個人方案。','SEO Pack'=>'SEO Pack','SEO Pack (Legacy)'=>'SEO Pack (舊版)','SEO support for page slug, page title, description and facebook and twitter social graph information. The HTML lang attribute is properly set.'=>'提供頁面 slug、頁面標題、描述以及 Facebook 和 Twitter 社交圖譜資訊的 SEO 支援。HTML lang 屬性已正確設定。','Multiple Languages'=>'多種語言','Add as many languages as you need for your project to go global. Publish your language only when all your translations are done.'=>'為專案走向全球新增所需數量的語言。請在所有翻譯完成後，再發佈您的語言。','Pro Add-ons'=>'專業附加元件','These addons extend your translation plugin and are available in the Business and Developer plans.'=>'這些附加元件可擴充您的翻譯外掛，適用於商業及開發者方案。','DeepL Automatic Translation'=>'DeepL 自動翻譯','Automatically translate your website through the DeepL API.'=>'透過 DeepL API 自動翻譯您的網站。','Prompts visitors to switch to their preferred language based on their browser settings or IP address and remembers the last visited language.'=>'根據訪客的瀏覽器設定或 IP 位址，提示訪客切換至其偏好語言，並記住上次造訪的語言。','Translator Accounts'=>'譯者帳號','Create translator accounts for new users or allow existing users that are not administrators to translate your website.'=>'為新使用者建立譯者帳號，或允許現有的非管理員使用者翻譯您的網站。','Browse As User Role'=>'以使用者角色瀏覽','Navigate your website just like a particular user role would. Really useful for dynamic content or hidden content that appears for particular users.'=>'如同特定使用者角色般瀏覽您的網站。對於動態內容或僅向特定使用者顯示的隱藏內容非常實用。','Navigation Based on Language'=>'依語言的導覽','Configure different menu items for different languages.'=>'為不同語言設定不同的選單項目。','Different Domain per Language'=>'每種語言使用不同網域','Connect separate domains or subdomains to each of your translated versions. Strengthen your brand’s local identity and boost SEO performance for every language you support.'=>'為每個翻譯版本連接獨立的網域或子網域。強化品牌的在地識別度，並提升每種支援語言的 SEO 成效。','Recommended Plugins'=>'推薦外掛','A short list of plugins you can use to extend your website.'=>'簡短列出可用於擴充網站的外掛。','Profile Builder'=>'Profile Builder','Capture more user information on the registration form with the help of Profile Builder\'s custom user profile fields and/or add an Email Confirmation process to verify your customers accounts.'=>'透過 Profile Builder 的自訂使用者資料欄位，在註冊表單中收集更多使用者資訊，以及/或新增電子郵件確認流程來驗證客戶的帳號。','Paid Member Subscriptions'=>'Paid Member Subscriptions','Accept user payments, create subscription plans and restrict content on your membership site.'=>'接受使用者付款、建立訂閱方案，並在會員網站上限制內容存取。','WP Webhooks Automator'=>'WP Webhooks Automator','Create no-code automations and workflows on your WordPress site. Easily connect your plugins, sites and apps together.'=>'在 WordPress 網站上建立無程式碼自動化流程與工作流程。輕鬆串連你的外掛、網站與應用程式。','Save Changes'=>'儲存變更','TranslatePress Errors'=>'TranslatePress 錯誤','There are no logged errors.'=>'目前沒有記錄的錯誤。','Change language'=>'變更語言','Website language selector'=>'網站語言選擇器','WordPress Translation Plugin'=>'WordPress 翻譯外掛','Available languages'=>'可用語言','Language Switcher update notice'=>'語言切換器更新通知','Legacy language switcher is currently enabled'=>'目前已啟用舊版語言切換器','We’ve upgraded the switcher for richer customization and a better user experience.<br>In order to use the new configurator, turn off <strong>Load legacy language switcher</strong>.'=>'我們已升級切換器，提供更豐富的自訂選項和更好的使用者體驗。<br>如要使用新的設定工具，請關閉<strong>載入舊版語言切換器</strong>。','Note: You can switch back anytime from <strong>Advanced Settings → <a href="%s">Troubleshooting</a></strong>.'=>'注意：您可以隨時從<strong>進階設定 → <a href="%s">疑難排解</a></strong>切換回去。','Enable the new switcher'=>'啟用新切換器','Your License Key is valid.'=>'您的授權金鑰有效。','Your License Key is invalid.'=>'您的授權金鑰無效。','Your License has expired.'=>'您的授權已過期。','Deactivate License'=>'停用授權','Add a license key'=>'新增授權金鑰','License Key'=>'授權金鑰','Manage your license in your %1$s.'=>'在您的%1$s中管理您的授權。','Account Page'=>'帳號頁面','Don’t have a TranslatePress AI License Key?'=>'沒有 TranslatePress AI 授權金鑰？','You can get one for %1$sfree%2$s, by creating a free account. It includes:'=>'只要建立免費帳號，即可%1$s免費%2$s取得一組。內容包括：','Access to TranslatePress AI for instant automatic translations'=>'使用 TranslatePress AI 進行即時自動翻譯','2000 AI words to translate automatically'=>'2000 個可自動翻譯的 AI 字數','Get a free License Today'=>'立即取得免費授權','Debug Information'=>'偵錯資訊','Debug Data for License Checking'=>'授權檢查的偵錯資料','Debug Data for License Activation'=>'授權啟用的偵錯資料','Get more AI words and unlock all features with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'取得更多 AI 字數，並使用 TranslatePress Pro 解鎖所有功能。','Upgrade now ↗'=>'立即升級 ↗','Already purchased a Premium version?'=>'已購買進階版本了嗎？','Go to your %1$s'=>'前往您的 %1$s','TranslatePress.com Account'=>'TranslatePress.com 帳號','Download & Install the Pro plugin'=>'下載並安裝 Pro 外掛程式','Learn More'=>'了解更多','Get a translation volume estimate with a detailed breakdown per page'=>'取得翻譯量預估，並提供每頁的詳細分項資料','Find how many translatable words are on your website'=>'查看您的網站上有多少可翻譯的字數','Enable Automatic Translation'=>'啟用自動翻譯','To use <strong>DeepL</strong> for automatic translation, activate this Pro add-on from the <a href="%1$s" target="_self" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>.'=>'若要使用 <strong>DeepL</strong> 進行自動翻譯，請從 <a href="%1$s" target="_self" title="%2$s">%2$s</a> 啟用此 Pro 附加元件。','<strong>DeepL</strong> automatic translation is available as a <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a>.'=>'<strong>DeepL</strong> 自動翻譯以 <a href="%1$s" target="_blank" title="%2$s">%2$s</a> 的形式提供。','By upgrading you\'ll get access to all paid add-ons, premium support and help fund the future development of TranslatePress.'=>'升級後即可使用所有付費附加元件、獲得進階支援，並協助 TranslatePress 的未來開發。','Please note that DeepL API usage is paid separately. See <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL pricing information</a>.'=>'請注意，DeepL API 的使用需另外付費。請參閱 <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL 定價資訊</a>。','TranslatePress Pro Add-ons'=>'TranslatePress Pro 附加元件','Test API credentials'=>'測試 API 憑證','Check if the selected translation engine is configured correctly.'=>'檢查所選的翻譯引擎是否設定正確。','Alternative Engines'=>'替代引擎','Switch to TranslatePress AI'=>'切換至 TranslatePress AI','Integrate machine translation directly with your WordPress website.'=>'直接將機器翻譯整合至您的 WordPress 網站。','More info'=>'更多資訊','Choose which engine you want to use in order to %1$s automatically translate your website.'=>'選擇您要使用的引擎，以便%1$s自動翻譯您的網站。','Automatic Translation Settings'=>'自動翻譯設定','AI Words Low Notification'=>'AI 字數不足通知','Receive an email notification when your TranslatePress AI word count drops below the specified threshold.'=>'當您的 TranslatePress AI 字數低於指定門檻時，接收電子郵件通知。','This feature is only available when using the TranslatePress AI translation engine.'=>'此功能僅在使用 TranslatePress AI 翻譯引擎時可用。','Notification Email'=>'通知電子郵件','The email address where the low AI words notification will be sent.'=>'接收 AI 字數不足通知的電子郵件地址。','Word Threshold'=>'字數門檻','words'=>'字','You will be notified when remaining AI words drop below this number.'=>'當剩餘 AI 字數低於此數字時，您將收到通知。','Automatically Translate Slugs'=>'自動翻譯 Slug','Generate automatic translations of slugs for posts, pages and Custom Post Types.<br/>The slugs will be automatically translated starting with the second refresh of each page.'=>'為文章、頁面和自訂文章類型自動產生 slug 翻譯。<br/>從每個頁面的第二次重新整理開始，slug 將會自動翻譯。','This feature is only available in the paid version. Upgrade TranslatePress and unlock more premium features.'=>'此功能僅於付費版本提供。升級 TranslatePress 以解鎖更多進階功能。','Requires <a href="%s" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank">SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'需要安裝並啟用 <a href="%s" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank">SEO Pack 附加元件</a>。','Upgrade now'=>'立即升級','Block Crawlers'=>'封鎖爬蟲','Block crawlers from triggering automatic translations on your website.<br>This will not prevent crawlers from accessing this site\'s pages.'=>'防止爬蟲在您的網站上觸發自動翻譯。<br>這不會阻止爬蟲存取此網站的頁面。','Limit machine translation / characters per day'=>'限制機器翻譯 / 每日字元數','Add a limit to the number of automatically translated characters so you can better budget your project.'=>'為自動翻譯的字元數設定上限，以便更好地規劃專案預算。','characters per day'=>'每日字元數','Today\'s Character Count: '=>'今日字元數： ','Log machine translation queries.'=>'記錄機器翻譯查詢。','Only enable for testing purposes. Can impact performance.<br>All records are stored in the wp_trp_machine_translation_log database table. Use a plugin like <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a> to browse the logs or directly from your database manager (PHPMyAdmin, etc.)'=>'僅供測試用途時啟用。可能會影響效能。<br>所有記錄都儲存在 wp_trp_machine_translation_log 資料庫資料表中。請使用如 <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a> 之類的外掛來瀏覽記錄，或直接透過您的資料庫管理工具 (PHPMyAdmin 等) 查看。','Test API Credentials'=>'測試 API 憑證','HTTP Referrer: '=>'HTTP Referrer: ','Use this HTTP Referrer if the API lets you restrict key usage from its Dashboard.'=>'如果 API 可讓您從其控制台限制金鑰的使用範圍，請使用這個 HTTP Referrer。','Response'=>'回應','Response Body'=>'回應主體','Entire Response From wp_remote_get():'=>'wp_remote_get() 的完整回應：','All Languages'=>'所有語言','Select the languages you wish to make your website available in.'=>'選取您希望網站支援的語言。','Formality'=>'正式程度','Code'=>'代碼','Slug'=>'Slug','Default'=>'預設','Formal'=>'正式','Informal'=>'非正式','Language'=>'語言','This language does not support formality. '=>'這個語言不支援正式程度。 ','Are you sure you want to remove this language?'=>'您確定要移除此語言嗎？','Custom Languages'=>'自訂語言','To Add more languages activate the Multiple Languages Addon'=>'若要新增更多語言，請啟用 Multiple Languages Addon。','You need an active license to add more languages. Verify in your %1$saccount%2$s that your license is valid'=>'您需要有效的授權才能新增更多語言。請在您的%1$s帳號%2$s中確認授權是否有效。','Please %1$senter your license%2$s key first to add more languages.'=>'請先%1$s輸入您的授權%2$s金鑰，才能新增更多語言。','Adding more than two languages is a paid feature. Upgrade TranslatePress and unlock more premium features.'=>'新增超過兩種語言是付費功能。升級 TranslatePress 以解鎖更多進階功能。','Website Languages'=>'網站語言','Default Language'=>'預設語言','Select the language your content is written in.'=>'選取您內容所使用的語言。','WARNING. Changing the default language will invalidate existing translations.'=>'警告：變更預設語言將會使現有翻譯失效。','Even changing from en_US to en_GB, because they are treated as two different languages.'=>'即使是從 en_US 變更為 en_GB 也一樣，因為它們會被視為兩種不同的語言。','In most cases changing the default flag is all it is needed: '=>'在大多數情況下，變更預設旗幟就是所需的一切： ','replace the default flag'=>'取代預設旗幟','Re-run Setup Wizard'=>'重新執行設定精靈','The Setup wizard allows you to quickly setup TranslatePress. You can initiate it at any time.'=>'設定精靈可讓您快速設定 TranslatePress。您可以隨時啟動它。','Language Settings'=>'語言設定','Use Native language name'=>'使用語言原生名稱','Check if you want to display languages in their native names. Otherwise, languages will be displayed in English.'=>'如果您希望以各語言的母語名稱顯示，請勾選此項目。否則，語言將以英文顯示。','Use a subdirectory for the default language'=>'為預設語言使用子目錄','Check if you want to add the subdirectory in the URL for the default language.</br>By checking this option, the default language seen by website visitors will become the first one in the "All Languages" list.'=>'如果您想要為預設語言在網址中加入子目錄，請勾選此項目。</br>勾選此選項後，網站訪客看到的預設語言將會變成「所有語言」清單中的第一個語言。','Force language in custom links'=>'在自訂連結中強制使用語言','Select Yes if you want to force custom links without language encoding to keep the currently selected language.'=>'如果您希望強制沒有語言編碼的自訂連結保留目前選取的語言，請選取「是」。','Shortcode '=>'shortcode ','Use shortcode on any page or widget.'=>'在任何頁面或小工具使用 shortcode。','You can also add the <a href="%s" title="Language Switcher Block Documentation">Language Switcher Block</a> in the WP Gutenberg Editor.'=>'你也可以在 WP Gutenberg 編輯器中加入 <a href="%s" title="Language Switcher Block Documentation">語言切換區塊</a>。','Menu item'=>'選單項目','Go to  %1$s Appearance -> Menus%2$s to add languages to the Language Switcher in any menu.'=>'前往  %1$s 外觀 -> 選單%2$s，將語言加入任何選單的語言切換器。','Learn more in our documentation.'=>'在我們的文件中了解更多。','Floating language selection'=>'浮動語言選擇','Add a floating dropdown that follows the user on every page.'=>'新增一個浮動下拉選單，跟隨使用者瀏覽每個頁面。','Show "Powered by TranslatePress"'=>'顯示「Powered by TranslatePress」','Show the small "Powered by TranslatePress" label in the floater language switcher.'=>'在浮動語言切換器中顯示「Powered by TranslatePress」小標籤。','5 Days to Better Multilingual Websites'=>'5 天打造更優質的多語言網站','%sJoin our FREE & EXCLUSIVE onboarding course%s and learn how to grow your multilingual traffic, reach international markets, and save time & money while getting the most out of TranslatePress!'=>'%s加入我們免費且專屬的入門課程%s，學習如何提升多語言流量、觸及國際市場，並在充分運用 TranslatePress 的同時節省時間與金錢！','Invalid email address'=>'電子郵件地址無效','Your email'=>'你的電子郵件','Sign me up!'=>'我要訂閱！','Sign up with your email address and receive a 5-part email guide to help you maximize the power of TranslatePress.'=>'使用你的電子郵件地址訂閱，即可收到 5 部分的電子郵件指南，協助你充分發揮 TranslatePress 的功能。','Dismiss email course notification'=>'關閉電子郵件課程通知','Hey %s,<br>Never miss an important update - opt in to our security and feature updates notifications, and non-sensitive diagnostic tracking.'=>'嘿，%s，<br>別錯過任何重要更新——請選擇接收我們的安全性與功能更新通知，以及非敏感的診斷追蹤。','Allow & Continue'=>'允許並繼續','Skip'=>'略過','This will allow TranslatePress to:'=>'這將允許 TranslatePress：','Your profile overview'=>'你的個人資料概覽','Name and email address'=>'名稱與電子郵件地址','Admin Notices'=>'管理員通知','Updates, announcements, marketing, no spam'=>'更新、公告、行銷，無垃圾郵件','Plugin status & settings'=>'外掛狀態與設定','Active, Deactivated, installed version and settings'=>'啟用、停用、已安裝版本與設定','Privacy Policy'=>'隱私權政策','Terms of Service'=>'服務條款','Support'=>'支援','Documentation'=>'說明文件','Add Extra AI Words'=>'新增額外 AI 字數','Optimize TranslatePress database tables'=>'最佳化 TranslatePress 資料庫資料表','<strong>IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong> Before performing this action it is strongly recommended to first backup the database.'=>'<strong>重要注意事項：</strong>執行此操作前，強烈建議先備份資料庫。','IMPORTANT: It is strongly recommended to first backup the database!! Are you sure you want to continue?'=>'重要：強烈建議先備份資料庫！！確定要繼續嗎？','Operations to perform'=>'要執行的操作','Remove CDATA for original and dictionary strings'=>'移除原始字串和字典字串的 CDATA','Removes CDATA from trp_original_strings and trp_dictionary_* tables.<br>This type of content should not be detected by TranslatePress. It might have been introduced in the database in older versions of the plugin.'=>'從 trp_original_strings 與 trp_dictionary_* 資料表中移除 CDATA。<br>這類內容不應被 TranslatePress 偵測到。它可能是由舊版外掛引入資料庫的。','Remove untranslated links from dictionary tables'=>'從字典資料表中移除未翻譯的連結','Removes untranslated links and images from all trp_dictionary_* tables. These tables contain translations for user-inputted strings such as post content, post title, menus etc.'=>'從所有 trp_dictionary_* 資料表中移除未翻譯的連結和圖片。這些資料表包含使用者輸入字串的翻譯，例如文章內容、文章標題、選單等。','Remove duplicate rows for gettext strings'=>'移除 gettext 字串的重複資料列','Cleans up all trp_gettext_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for themes and plugin strings.'=>'清除所有 trp_gettext_* 資料表中的重複資料列。這些資料表包含佈景主題和外掛字串的翻譯。','Remove duplicate rows for dictionary strings'=>'移除字典字串的重複資料列','Cleans up all trp_dictionary_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for user-inputted strings such as post content, post title, menus etc.'=>'清除所有 trp_dictionary_* 資料表中的重複資料列。這些資料表包含使用者輸入字串的翻譯，例如文章內容、文章標題、選單等。','Remove duplicate rows for original dictionary strings'=>'移除原始字典字串的重複資料列','Cleans up all trp_original_strings table of duplicate rows. This table contains strings in the default language, without any translation.<br>The trp_original_meta table, which contains meta information that refers to the post parent’s ID, is also regenerated.<br>Such duplicates can appear in exceptional situations of unexpected behavior.'=>'清除 trp_original_strings 資料表中的所有重複資料列。此資料表包含預設語言的字串，不含任何翻譯。<br>trp_original_meta 資料表（包含參照上層文章 ID 的中繼資料）也會重新產生。<br>這類重複資料可能在發生未預期的異常行為時出現。','Replace gettext strings that have original ID NULL with the correct original IDs'=>'將原始 ID 為 NULL 的 gettext 字串替換為正確的原始 ID','Fixes an edge case issue where some gettext strings have the original ID incorrectly set to NULL, causing problems in the Translation Editor.<br>This operation corrects the original IDs in the trp_gettext_* tables.<br>Only check this option if you encountered an issue in the Translation Editor where clicking the green pencil did not bring up the gettext string for translation in the left sidebar.<br>Otherwise, please leave this option unchecked because it\'s an intensive operation.'=>'修正某些 gettext 字串的原始 ID 被錯誤設為 NULL 的邊緣案例問題，此問題會造成翻譯編輯器出現問題。<br>此操作會修正 trp_gettext_* 資料表中的原始 ID。<br>只有當您在翻譯編輯器中遇到點擊綠色鉛筆後，左側邊欄未顯示該 gettext 字串供翻譯的問題時，才勾選此選項。<br>否則，請勿勾選此選項，因為這是一項耗費資源的作業。','Optimize Database'=>'最佳化資料庫','TranslatePress Database Updater'=>'TranslatePress Database Updater','Updating TranslatePress tables. Please leave this window open.'=>'正在更新 TranslatePress 資料表。請保持此視窗開啟。','The inactive languages will still be visible and active for the admin. For other users they won\'t be visible in the language switchers and won\'t be accessible either.'=>'非啟用中的語言對管理員仍然可見且作用中。對其他使用者而言，這些語言不會顯示在語言切換器中，也無法存取。','unknown'=>'未知','<strong>Extra Languages add-on</strong> requires TranslatePress version %1$s or higher. You are currently using version %2$s. Please update TranslatePress to enable this feature.'=>'<strong>Extra Languages 附加元件</strong>需要 TranslatePress 版本 %1$s 或更高版本。你目前使用的版本為 %2$s。請更新 TranslatePress 以啟用此功能。','Automatic and manual slug translation changes performed when <strong>TranslatePress - Multilingual</strong> 2.8.4 was active had to be removed because of some issues with that version. All slug translations from before that version are now in use. Thank you for understanding!'=>'由於 <strong>TranslatePress - Multilingual</strong> 2.8.4 版本存在某些問題，必須移除在該版本運作期間執行的自動和手動 slug 翻譯變更。該版本之前的所有 slug 翻譯現已恢復使用。感謝您的諒解！','If you absolutely need them, the removed translations can be found in tables trp_slug_original_obsolete and trp_slug_translation_obsolete.'=>'如果你確實需要這些翻譯，可以在 trp_slug_original_obsolete 和 trp_slug_translation_obsolete 資料表中找到。','View Docs'=>'查看文件','Assign different domains or subdomains to each language. When visitors access these domains, TranslatePress loads the appropriate language translation directly without redirecting.'=>'為每種語言指派不同的網域或子網域。當訪客存取這些網域時，TranslatePress 會直接載入對應的語言翻譯，無需重新導向。','Example: %1$s for English, %2$s for Spanish, %3$s for French.'=>'範例：英文使用 %1$s、西班牙文使用 %2$s、法文使用 %3$s。','Before enabling:'=>'啟用前：','Ensure your domains are registered, pointed to your server, and have SSL certificates configured.'=>'請確保你的網域已註冊、指向你的伺服器，並已設定 SSL 憑證。','Domain'=>'網域','Map this language to a different domain or sub-domain.'=>'將此語言對應至不同的網域或子網域。','https://example.com'=>'https://example.com','Prefill with current domain'=>'以目前網域預填','Check DNS'=>'檢查 DNS','Checking DNS...'=>'正在檢查 DNS…','DNS is correctly configured!'=>'DNS 設定正確！','DNS check failed. Please verify your domain configuration.'=>'DNS 檢查失敗。請確認你的網域設定。','This domain is already assigned to another language.'=>'此網域已指派給其他語言。','<strong>Different Domain per Language add-on</strong> requires TranslatePress version %1$s or higher. You are currently using version %2$s. Please update TranslatePress to enable this feature.'=>'<strong>Different Domain per Language 附加元件</strong>需要 TranslatePress 版本 %1$s 或更高版本。你目前使用的版本為 %2$s。請更新 TranslatePress 以啟用此功能。','Note: This option is disabled when Different Domain for Language addon is active.'=>'注意：當 Different Domain for Language 附加元件啟用時，此選項會停用。','Different Domain per Language: Domain is required when domain mapping is enabled. The toggle has been disabled for languages with empty domains.'=>'Different Domain per Language：啟用網域對應時必須提供網域。已停用網域為空之語言的切換開關。','Different Domain per Language: The same domain cannot be assigned to multiple languages. The toggle has been disabled for duplicate domains.'=>'Different Domain per Language：同一個網域無法指派給多個語言。已停用重複網域的切換開關。','Different Domain per Language: A language domain cannot be the same as the main site URL. The toggle has been disabled for the matching domain.'=>'Different Domain per Language：語言網域不能與主要網站 URL 相同。已停用相符網域的切換開關。','Please enter a domain.'=>'請輸入網域。','Invalid domain format.'=>'網域格式無效。','Could not reach domain: %s'=>'無法連線至網域：%s','Domain returned HTTP status %d.'=>'網域傳回 HTTP 狀態碼 %d。','Domain is reachable!'=>'網域可以連線！','Limit this menu item to the following languages'=>'將此選單項目限制為以下語言','Date format'=>'日期格式','Customize the date formatting per each translated language.<br/>Leave empty for default WP setting or see more information <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">here</a>'=>'為每個翻譯語言自訂日期格式。<br/>留空以使用預設 WP 設定，或<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/" title="Formatting Date and Time" target="_blank">在此處</a>查看更多資訊。','To edit an existing TranslatePress language, input the language code and fill in only the columns you want to overwrite (e.g. Language name, Flag).<br>You can also add new custom languages. They will be available under General settings, All Languages list, where the URL slug can be edited.'=>'若要編輯現有的 TranslatePress 語言，請輸入語言代碼，並僅填寫您想要覆寫的欄位（例如語言名稱、旗標）。<br>您也可以新增自訂語言。這些語言將會顯示在「一般設定」的「所有語言」清單中，您可以在該處編輯 URL slug。','For custom flag, first upload the image in media library then paste the URL.<br>Changing or deleting a custom language will impact translations and site URL\'s.<br>The Language code and the ISO Code should contain only alphabetical values, numerical values, "-" and "_".<br>The ISO Codes can be found on <a href = "https://cloud.google.com/translate/docs/languages" target = "_blank">Google ISO Codes</a> and <a href = "https://www.deepl.com/docs-api/translating-text/" target = "_blank">DeepL Target Codes</a>.'=>'若要使用自訂旗標，請先將圖片上傳至媒體庫，然後貼上 URL。<br>變更或刪除自訂語言將會影響翻譯和網站 URL。<br>語言代碼和 ISO 代碼只能包含字母、數字、「-」和「_」。<br>ISO 代碼可於 <a href = "https://cloud.google.com/translate/docs/languages" target = "_blank">Google ISO 代碼</a> 和 <a href = "https://www.deepl.com/docs-api/translating-text/" target = "_blank">DeepL 目標代碼</a> 查詢。','Language code'=>'語言代碼','Language name'=>'語言名稱','Native name'=>'原生名稱','ISO Code'=>'ISO 代碼','Flag URL'=>'旗標 URL','Text RTL'=>'RTL 文字','Custom language'=>'自訂語言','Disable dynamic translation'=>'停用動態翻譯','It disables detection of strings displayed dynamically using JavaScript. <br/>Strings loaded via a server side AJAX call will still be translated.'=>'停用偵測使用 JavaScript 動態顯示的字串。 <br/>透過伺服器端 AJAX 呼叫載入的字串仍會被翻譯。','Disable translation for gettext strings'=>'停用 gettext 字串的翻譯','Gettext Strings are strings outputted by themes and plugins. <br> Translating these types of strings through TranslatePress can be unnecessary if they are already translated using the .po/.mo translation file system.<br>Enabling this option can improve the page load performance of your site in certain cases. The disadvantage is that you can no longer edit gettext translations using TranslatePress, nor benefit from automatic translation on these strings.'=>'Gettext 字串是由佈景主題和外掛輸出的字串。<br> 如果這類字串已經使用 .po/.mo 翻譯檔案系統完成翻譯，透過 TranslatePress 再次翻譯可能是不必要的。<br>啟用此選項在某些情況下可改善網站的頁面載入效能。缺點是您將無法再使用 TranslatePress 編輯 gettext 翻譯，這些字串也無法使用自動翻譯。','Gettext Strings translation is disabled'=>'Gettext 字串翻譯已停用','To enable it go to '=>'若要啟用，請前往 ','TranslatePress->Advanced Settings->Debug->Disable translation for gettext strings'=>'TranslatePress->進階設定->偵錯->停用 Gettext 字串翻譯',' and uncheck the Checkbox.'=>' 並取消勾選核取方塊。','Dismiss'=>'關閉','Exclude translated links from sitemap'=>'從 sitemap 排除翻譯連結','Do not include translated links in sitemaps generated by SEO plugins.<br/>Requires <a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=miscellaneous" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'請勿將翻譯後的連結包含在 SEO 外掛產生的 sitemaps 中。<br/>需要安裝並啟用<a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=miscellaneous" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack 附加元件</a>。','Disable post container tags for post title'=>'停用文章標題的容器標籤','It disables search indexing the post title in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the title of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'這會停用翻譯語言中文章標題的搜尋索引。<br/>當文章標題不允許 HTML 因而導致頁面損壞時，此功能非常實用。','Disable post container tags for post content'=>'停用文章內容的容器標籤','It disables search indexing the post content in translated languages.<br/>Useful when the content of the post doesn\'t allow HTML thus breaking the page.'=>'這會停用翻譯語言中文章內容的搜尋索引。<br/>當文章內容不允許 HTML 因而導致頁面損壞時，此功能非常實用。','Do not translate certain paths'=>'不翻譯特定路徑','Choose what paths can be translated. Supports wildcard at the end of the path.<br>For example, to exclude https://example.com/some/path you can either use the rule /some/path/ or /some/*.<br>Enter each rule on it\'s own line. To exclude the home page use {{home}}.'=>'選擇哪些路徑可以翻譯。支援在路徑結尾使用萬用字元。<br>例如，要排除 https://example.com/some/path，你可以使用規則 /some/path/ 或 /some/*。<br>每條規則請輸入於獨立一行。若要排除首頁，請使用 {home}。','Exclude Paths From Translation'=>'從翻譯排除路徑','Translate Only Certain Paths'=>'只翻譯特定路徑','Enable the hreflang x-default tag for language:'=>'啟用語言的 hreflang x-default 標籤：','Enables the hreflang="x-default" for an entire language. See documentation for more details.'=>'為整個語言啟用 hreflang="x-default"。詳情請參閱說明文件。','Translate numbers and numerals'=>'翻譯數字與數值','Enable translation of numbers ( e.g. phone numbers)'=>'啟用數字翻譯（例如電話號碼）','Selector'=>'選取器','Exclude from dynamic translation'=>'從動態翻譯排除','Do not dynamically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated using JavaScript.<br/>These strings will still be translated on the server side if possible.'=>'不要動態翻譯在符合這些選取器的 HTML 節點中找到的字串。<br>排除符合這些選取器之 HTML 節點的所有子節點，使其不會透過 JavaScript 進行翻譯。<br/>如果可行，這些字串仍會在伺服器端進行翻譯。','Gettext String'=>'Gettext 字串','Exclude Gettext Strings'=>'排除 Gettext 字串','Exclude these strings from being translated as Gettext strings by TranslatePress. Leave the domain empty to take into account any Gettext string.<br/>Can still be translated through po/mo files.'=>'將這些字串排除在 TranslatePress 的 Gettext 字串翻譯之外。將網域留白以納入任何 Gettext 字串。<br/>仍可透過 po/mo 檔案進行翻譯。','Exclude selectors only from automatic translation'=>'僅將選擇器排除於自動翻譯之外','Do not automatically translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being automatically translated.<br>Manual translation of these strings is still possible.'=>'不要自動翻譯在符合這些選取器的 HTML 節點中找到的字串。<br>排除符合這些選取器之 HTML 節點的所有子節點，使其不會自動翻譯。<br>這些字串仍可以手動翻譯。','Exclude selectors from translation'=>'將選擇器排除於翻譯之外','Do not translate strings that are found in html nodes matching these selectors.<br>Excludes all the children of HTML nodes matching these selectors from being translated.<br>These strings cannot be translated manually nor automatically.'=>'不要翻譯在符合這些選取器的 HTML 節點中找到的字串。<br>排除符合這些選取器之 HTML 節點的所有子節點，使其不被翻譯。<br>這些字串無法手動或自動翻譯。','String'=>'字串','Exclude strings from automatic translation'=>'將字串排除在自動翻譯之外','Do not automatically translate these strings (ex. names, technical words...)<br>Paragraphs containing these strings will still be translated except for the specified part.'=>'不要自動翻譯這些字串（例如名稱、技術詞彙……）。<br>包含這些字串的段落仍會翻譯，但指定的部分除外。','Fix broken HTML'=>'修復損壞的 HTML','General attempt to fix broken or missing HTML on translated pages.<br/>'=>'一般嘗試修復翻譯頁面上損壞或遺漏的 HTML。<br/>','Force slash at end of home url:'=>'強制在首頁 URL 結尾加上斜線：','Ads a slash at the end of the home_url() function'=>'在 home_url() 函式結尾加上斜線','Show Both (recommended)'=>'兩者都顯示（建議）','Remove Country Locale'=>'移除國家/地區語系','Remove Region Independent Locale'=>'移除區域獨立語系','Remove duplicate hreflang'=>'移除重複的 hreflang','Choose which hreflang tags will appear on your website.<br/>We recommend showing both types of hreflang tags as indicated by <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/advanced/crawling/localized-versions" title="Google Crawling" target="_blank">Google documentation</a>.<br/>Removing Country Locale when having multiple Country Locales of the same language (ex. English UK and English US) will result in showing one hreflang tag with link to just one of the region locales for that language.'=>'選擇哪些 hreflang 標籤會顯示在您的網站上。<br/>我們建議顯示這兩種 hreflang 標籤，如<a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/advanced/crawling/localized-versions" title="Google Crawling" target="_blank">Google 說明文件</a>所述。<br/>當同一語言有多個國家/地區語系（例如：英文（英國）與英文（美國））時，移除國家/地區語系將導致只顯示一個 hreflang 標籤，且連結僅指向該語言的其中一個地區語系。','Default (example: en-US, fr-CA, etc.)'=>'預設（例如：en-US、fr-CA 等）','Regional (example: en, fr, es, etc.)'=>'區域（例如：en、fr、es 等）','HTML Lang Attribute Format'=>'HTML Lang 屬性格式','Change lang attribute of the html tag to a format that includes country regional or not. <br>In HTML, the lang attribute (<html lang="en-US">)  should be used to  specify the language of text content so that the  browser can correctly display or process  your content (eg. for  hyphenation, styling, spell checking, etc).'=>'將 html 標籤的 lang 屬性變更為包含或不包含國家/地區的格式。<br>在 HTML 中，lang 屬性（<html lang="en-US">）應用於指定文字內容的語言，以便瀏覽器能正確顯示或處理您的內容（例如斷字、樣式設定、拼字檢查等）。','Load legacy Language Switcher'=>'載入舊版語言切換器','Applies to all types of language switchers (floating, shortcode, and menu). When enabled, the site will revert to using the original Language Switcher configured in the General Settings tab, replacing the new customizable version. Your existing switcher settings will remain saved, but they will be ignored while this option is active.'=>'適用於所有類型的語言切換器（浮動、shortcode 和選單）。啟用後，網站將恢復使用「一般設定」分頁中設定的原始語言切換器，取代新的可自訂版本。您現有的切換器設定將繼續儲存，但在此選項啟用期間會被忽略。','Load legacy SEO Pack Add-On'=>'載入舊版 SEO Pack 附加元件','In case the recent migration to the new slug rewrite is causing trouble, set this to Yes to use the old method <br> Please <a href="https://translatepress.com/support/open-ticket/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=troubleshooting" target="_blank">open a support ticket</a> letting us know of the issues you are having.'=>'如果最近移轉至新的 slug 重寫規則造成問題，請將此選項設為「是」以使用舊方法 <br> 請<a href="https://translatepress.com/support/open-ticket/?utm_source=tp-advanced&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=troubleshooting" target="_blank">開啟支援票證</a>，讓我們知道您遇到的問題。','Manual Translation Only'=>'僅手動翻譯','TranslatePress pro-actively scans and saves strings in the database when users access translated pages. <br>This setting disables this functionality and only allows translation and string saving when inside the Translation Editor. <br>Also disables machine translation outside the Translation Editor, giving you better control over character spending, by translating only the pages you visit in the Translation Editor.'=>'TranslatePress 會在使用者存取翻譯頁面時，主動掃描並將字串儲存至資料庫。<br>此設定會停用這項功能，僅允許在翻譯編輯器內進行翻譯和儲存字串。<br>同時也會停用翻譯編輯器外部的機器翻譯，只翻譯您在翻譯編輯器中瀏覽的頁面，讓您更能控制字元用量。','Open language switcher only on click'=>'僅在點擊時開啟語言切換器','Open the language switcher shortcode by clicking on it instead of hovering.<br> Close it by clicking on it, anywhere else on the screen or by pressing the escape key. This will affect only the shortcode language switcher.'=>'透過點擊而非懸停來開啟語言切換器 shortcode。<br> 點擊該元素、畫面其他位置，或按下 Esc 鍵即可關閉。這只會影響 shortcode 語言切換器。','Show opposite language in the language switcher'=>'在語言切換器中顯示另一種語言','Transforms the language switcher into a button showing the other available language, not the current one.<br> Only works when there are exactly two languages, the default one and a translation one.<br>This will affect the shortcode language switcher and floating language switcher as well.<br> To achieve this in menu language switcher go to Appearance->Menus->Language Switcher and select Opposite Language.'=>'將語言切換器變更為顯示另一個可用語言（而非目前語言）的按鈕。<br> 僅在恰好有兩種語言（預設語言和翻譯語言）時有效。<br>這也會影響 shortcode 語言切換器和浮動語言切換器。<br> 若要在選單語言切換器中達成此效果，請前往「外觀->選單->語言切換器」並選取「另一種語言」。','<a href="%s">Click here</a> to access the database optimization tool.'=>'<a href="%s">點擊這裡</a>以存取資料庫最佳化工具。','It helps remove possible duplicate translations, clear unnecessary data and repair possible metadata issues.'=>'可協助移除可能的重複翻譯、清除不必要的資料，並修復可能的中繼資料問題。','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Here</a> you can observe the last 5 SQL errors relevant to TranslatePress if they exist.'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank">這裡</a>可以查看與 TranslatePress 相關的最後 5 筆 SQL 錯誤（如果存在的話）。','Troubleshooting'=>'疑難排解','Exclude Gettext strings'=>'排除 Gettext 字串','Debug'=>'偵錯','Custom languages'=>'自訂語言','Miscellaneous options'=>'其他選項','Exclude strings & pages'=>'排除字串與頁面','Automatic Translation Memory'=>'自動翻譯記憶體','Serve same translation for similar text. The strings need to have a percentage of 95% similarity.<br>Helps prevent losing existing translation when correcting typos or making minor adjustments to the original text. <br>If a translation already exists for a very similar original string, it will automatically be used for the current original string.<br>Does not work when making changes to a text that is part of a translation block unless the new text is manually merged again in a translation block.<br>Each string needs to have a minimum of 50 characters.'=>'為相似文字提供相同翻譯。字串必須達到 95% 的相似度。<br>有助於在修正錯字或對原始文字進行微調時，避免遺失現有翻譯。 <br>若已有與目前原始字串非常相似的字串翻譯，將自動套用到目前的原始字串。<br>當修改屬於翻譯區塊一部分的文字時，此功能不會生效，除非新文字再次手動合併到翻譯區塊中。<br>每個字串必須至少包含 50 個字元。','WARNING: This feature can negatively impact page loading times in secondary languages, particularly with large databases (for example websites with a lot of pages or products). If you experience slow loading times, disable this and try again.'=>'警告：此功能可能會對次要語言的頁面載入時間造成負面影響，特別是在資料庫龐大的情況下（例如擁有大量頁面或商品的網站）。如果您遇到載入速度變慢的情況，請停用此功能後再試一次。','Fix missing dynamic content'=>'修正遺失的動態內容','May help fix missing content inserted using JavaScript. <br> It shows dynamically inserted content in original language for a moment before the translation request is finished.'=>'可能有助於修正使用 JavaScript 插入的遺失內容。<br> 在翻譯請求完成前，會短暫顯示以原始語言動態插入的內容。','Filter Gettext wrapping from post content and title'=>'過濾文章內容與標題中的 Gettext 包裝標記','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post content and post title. Does not affect previous post content. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'過濾所有已更新文章內容及標題中的 Gettext 包裝標記（例如 #!trpst#trp-gettext）。不會影響先前的文章內容。 <br/><strong>建議在開啟前先備份資料庫。</strong>','Filter Gettext wrapping from post meta'=>'過濾文章中繼資料中的 Gettext 包裝標記','Filters gettext wrapping such as #!trpst#trp-gettext from all updated post meta. Does not affect previous post meta. <br/><strong>Database backup is recommended before switching on.</strong>'=>'過濾所有已更新文章中繼資料中的 Gettext 包裝標記（例如 #!trpst#trp-gettext）。不會影響先前的文章中繼資料。 <br/><strong>建議在開啟前先備份資料庫。</strong>','Google Translate v2'=>'Google Translate v2','Google Translate API Key'=>'Google Translate API 金鑰','Add your API Key here...'=>'在此輸入您的 API 金鑰...','Visit <a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">this link</a> to see how you can set up an API key, <strong>control API costs</strong> and set HTTP referrer restrictions.'=>'造訪<a href="https://cloud.google.com/docs/authentication/api-keys" target="_blank">此連結</a>以了解如何設定 API 金鑰、<strong>控管 API 費用</strong>以及設定 HTTP 參照網址限制。','Your HTTP referrer is: %s'=>'您的 HTTP 參照網址為：%s','There was an error on the server processing your Google Translate key.'=>'伺服器處理您的 Google Translate 金鑰時發生錯誤。','There was an error with your Google Translate key.'=>'您的 Google Translate 金鑰發生錯誤。','Please check your TranslatePress license key.'=>'請檢查您的 TranslatePress 授權金鑰。','TranslatePress AI'=>'TranslatePress AI','No Active License Detected for this website.'=>'未偵測到適用於此網站的有效授權。','In order to enable Automatic Translation using TranslatePress AI, you need a license key by creating a free account.'=>'若要使用 TranslatePress AI 啟用自動翻譯，您需要建立免費帳戶以取得授權金鑰。','Create your Free Account'=>'建立免費帳號',' or '=>' 或 ','Enter your license key'=>'輸入你的授權金鑰',' Or %1$spurchase one here%2$s'=>' 或%1$s在此購買%2$s','Your free account includes: '=>'免費帳號包含： ','Get more AI Words and unlock all AI features with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'取得更多 AI 字數，並使用 TranslatePress Pro 解鎖所有 AI 功能。','You have a valid %s <strong>license</strong>.'=>'你擁有有效的 %s <strong>授權</strong>。',' words remaining. '=>' 個字剩餘。 ','Recheck'=>'重新檢查','Rechecking...'=>'正在重新檢查...','Done.'=>'完成。','Manage your license & quota on the %s'=>'在 %s 管理你的授權和配額','TranslatePress.com Account Page'=>'TranslatePress.com 帳號頁面','SEO support for page slug, page title, description and Facebook and Twitter social graph information. The HTML lang attribute is properly set.'=>'支援頁面 slug、頁面標題、描述，以及 Facebook 與 Twitter 社交圖譜資訊的 SEO。HTML lang 屬性已正確設定。','Enable Modules'=>'啟用模組','Enable Add-on modules to extend TranslatePress and enhance the functionality of your translated site.'=>'啟用附加模組來擴充 TranslatePress，並提升翻譯網站的功能。','More functionality with TranslatePress Pro.'=>'使用 TranslatePress Pro 獲得更多功能。','Already a Pro User?'=>'已經是 Pro 使用者了嗎？','Activate License Key'=>'啟用授權金鑰','This add-on is not available on your current plan.'=>'此附加模組在你目前的方案中無法使用。','Continue'=>'繼續','The link you followed has expired. Please reload the page and try again.'=>'你點擊的連結已過期。請重新載入頁面後再試一次。','A valid license is required to enable Automatic Translation.'=>'必須擁有有效授權才能啟用自動翻譯。','Your license key is disabled for this URL. Re-enable it from <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=tp-onboarding&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=tp-ai">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> Manage Sites.'=>'你的授權金鑰已在此 URL 停用。請前往 <a target="_blank" href="https://translatepress.com/account/?utm_source=tp-onboarding&utm_medium=client-site&utm_campaign=tp-ai">https://translatepress.com/account</a> -> 管理網站重新啟用。','<p><strong>License key mismatch.</strong> The license you entered doesn\'t match the TranslatePress version you have installed.</p><p>Please check that you\'ve installed the correct version for your license from your TranslatePress account.</p>'=>'<p><strong>授權金鑰不相符。</strong>你輸入的授權金鑰與已安裝的 TranslatePress 版本不符。</p><p>請確認你已從 TranslatePress 帳號安裝與授權相符的正確版本。</p>','Automatically tran